creator: Scanbot Scanner SDK
descriptionHtml:
Turn any smartphone, tablet, or wearable device into an easy-to-use, fast, and reliable Barcode Scanner with the Scanbot SDK – create the kind of customer and employee satisfaction that makes all the difference.

This App demonstrates the speed and reliability our customers experience when integrating the Scanbot SDK into their mobile or web apps. Integratable in just one day, the Scanbot SDK covers all common 1D & 2D barcodes and works completely offline – without requiring a connection to any third-party server.

Our cutting-edge machine learning- and computer vision-based technology offers a broad range of features and benefits to any company with Mobile Barcode Scanning needs:

High-Speed Scanning
A barcode scanning speed of 0.2 seconds "WOWs" users and makes them enjoy using your app. Capture and extract data from multiple barcodes in one go.

Reliability
The Scanbot SDK can scan blurred and damaged barcodes from almost any angle, even in poor lighting conditions. Even scanning tiny barcodes or codes more than 2 meters away is no problem for the Scanbot SDK – making failed scans a thing of the past.

Unlimited Scanning
Since we are never connected to your app, we can't and don't want to track any volume variables - our customers can scan as much as they want without being penalized for their growing use case.

All common 1D & 2D Barcodes
The Scanbot SDK supports any barcode you need for your individual use case. We are the one trusted partner you need for all your Mobile Barcode Scanning needs:
- Aztec
- Codabar
- Code 39
- Code 93
- Code 128
- Data Matrix
- EAN-8
- EAN-13
- ITF
- MSI Plessey
- PDF 417
- QR Code
- UPC-A
- UPC-E
- RSS 14
- RSS Expanded

Do you want to test the Scanbot SDK in your mobile or web app? No Problem! You can simply sign up for a free 7-day Trial License at https://scanbot.io/trial/. Our support engineers will support you on your way to a hassle-free integration of Mobile Data Capture into your apps.

The Scanbot SDK is trusted by 200+ enterprises worldwide and valued by developers and users alike. Learn more about the Scanbot SDK on our website https://scanbot.io/.
descriptionShort: Turn mobile devices into fast & reliable Barcode Scanners with the Scanbot SDK

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: With the Scanbot SDK: Barcode Scanning App, we introduce our latest Barcode Scanning features. With different modes, such as batch and multiple scanning, as well as scanning of tiny and distant barcodes, we have created the most reliable barcode scanning solution for users with various use cases. Through an innovative AR overlay, they can now also see which barcode they are scanning - in just 0.2 seconds.
